#

Tropical Fruit Salad

10 min
$10
120 kcal
Difficulty: 5%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-FreeVegan

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Salad

Tags:

EasyHealthyRefreshing

Description

A refreshing and vibrant mix of tropical fruits to brighten your day!

Ingredients

  • pineapple: 1 cup, diced
  • mango: 1 cup, diced
  • kiwi: 2, sliced
  • strawberries: 1 cup, halved
  • blueberries: 1 cup
  • banana: 1, sliced
  • lime juice: 2 tablespoons
  • honey: 1 tablespoon
  • mint leaves: a handful, for garnish
